<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/21170904-michael">Michael</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Not at all, this book can be read without reading any other David Gemmell books and is a wonderful introduction to his writing style if you haven&apos;t re<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Not at all, this book can be read without reading any other David Gemmell books and is a wonderful introduction to his writing style if you haven't read any of his works at all. Definitely make sure you read Midnight Falcon after it too.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
